headline: Conagra will seek to mitigate steel tariffs’ impact on cans, CFO says
summary: The branded snack and frozen food company’s CFO spoke at a conference Tuesday, just days after President Trump announced he would raise steel and aluminum tariffs from 25% to 50%.
